      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hmm, none of the GCSClient API mentions anything about \"Upload\" so I don\u0027t think that really fits.\n\nI would have added these as additional methods on GCSClient, but then every impl would need to add them as well, which seems like a lot of trouble. Maybe instead we should have a smaller GCSClientImpl interface that only provides FileReader, FileWriter, AllFilesInDirectory, DeleteFile, and Bucket; and use an adapter to provide DoesFileExist, GetFileContents, SetFileContents, WithWriter, and WithGzipWriter?",
